| `35f3278` | **Defect #2**: GAMG+GaussSeidel p-solver diverged (Initial=1 → Final=NaN) on first timestep on noSlip cylinder geometry. checkMesh reported clean, Codex reviewed fvSolution static content, but runtime interaction between smoother + BC. Fix: PCG+DIC for p; endTime 200s→10s; maxCo 0.5→1.0 to bring projected wall from 40h → ~2.3h. |
| `7d79b04`, `2cca653`, `558f76d` | Doc commits — DEC frontmatter refresh, RETRO addendum, intake TEMPLATE.yaml |
| `e8b92ed` | **Defects #3+#4**: (#3) cylinder extractor gated on U/Cx/Cy field-file existence, but primary path (forceCoeffs + sets) doesn't need those. Fix: lift cylinder extractor above field-file gate in `_parse_writeobjects_fields`. (#4) `_copy_postprocess_fields` sort-key `sort -t/ -k1 -n` fell back to lexical on decimal time dirs, picked `5.998936` as "latest" over `10.000003`. Fix: awk-tag + numeric sort. |
