   207	) -> Optional[str]:
   208	    """Return `turbulence_model` from whitelist.yaml for the named case.
   209	
   210	    DEC-V61-053 Batch B1: whitelist may demand a specific model (e.g. `laminar`
   211	    for cylinder at Re=100 in the 2D Karman shedding regime). The historic
   212	    `_turbulence_model_for_solver` heuristic ignored whitelist and hardcoded
   213	    kOmegaSST for BODY_IN_CHANNEL EXTERNAL, silently over-dissipating the
   214	    wake. Callers should prefer this value when present and fall back to
   215	    the heuristic only when absent.
   216	
